Data Visualization¶

Visualize prosper Loan Data¶

In this project I want to visualize and get some insights about prosper Loan Data because I'm interesed in banking and I want to deploy my anaylsis knowledge on it. Our data related to peer to peer lending which is a way to connect borrower to lenders, the prosper is a platfrom that let people to invest in loans or borrow money. We have 113937 (check the code below) loans in our dataset and 81 columns for each loan.

Our dataset has 113937 loans and 81 column which containg the features of the dataset.
